00:13:19,461 --> 00:13:20,868
Adjugé à Jim !

247
00:13:21,938 --> 00:13:22,910
Adjugé !

248
00:13:24,034 --> 00:13:25,565
Amusez-vous bien.

249
00:13:26,370 --> 00:13:30,064
