00:19:04,181 --> 00:19:05,170
- 325.
- 325.

353
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:06,401
- 350 !
- 350.

354
00:19:06,521 --> 00:19:08,392
- 350 et un centime.
- 350 et un centime.

355
00:19:08,512 --> 00:19:09,832
- 400.
- 400...

356
00:19:09,952 --> 00:19:12,134
- 400 et un centime.
- 400 et un centime.

357
00:19:12,254 --> 00:19:13,951
- 500.
- 500,500...

358
00:19:14,071 --> 00:19:16,643
- 500 et un centime.
- 500 et un centime.

359
00:19:16,763 --> 00:19:18,035
Un million !

360
00:19:18,195 --> 00:19:19,575
- 700.
- 700.

361
00:19:19,695 --> 00:19:21,383
700 et un centime.

362
00:19:25,022 --> 00:19:25,834
1,000.

363
00:19:27,883 --> 00:19:29,126
Ça les vaut pas.

364
00:19:29,246 --> 00:19:31,742
1,000 $, une fois,
1,000 $, deux fois.

365
00:19:31,862 --> 00:19:33,361
Adjugé pour 1,000 $ !

366
00:19:38,892 --> 00:19:40,179
Félicitations.

367
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:57,102
Non. Finalement, non.

